title: DPS BestOf
itunes:title: DPS BestOf
description:
On Today Dan Patrick Show, Ross Tucker fills in for DP and recaps the draft with Pro Football Focus' Mike Renner. Why did so many of the QBs fall. Ed Marinaro joins Ross to talk about his viral moment of announcing the Vikings pick at the draft. And Eagles GM Howie Roseman tells us about trading up for AJ Brown.
